\p
\v 30 \add As for\add* God, his way \add is\add* perfect: the word of the LORD is tried: he \add is\add* a buckler to all those that trust in him.
\p
\v 31 For who \add is\add* God save the LORD? or who \add is\add* a rock save our God?
\p
